{"word":"G1591 - ἐκμάσσω - ekmássō - ek-mas'-so - Wipe","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐκμάσσω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">ekmássō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ek-mas'-so</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Wipe</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - துடை"},{"paragraph":"to wipe off, to wipe away"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1537 - ἐκ - ek - ek/1537\">G1537</a> and the base of <a href=\"#/G3145 - μασσάομαι - massáomai - mas-sah'-om-ahee/3145\">G3145</a>; to <i>knead out</i>, that is, (by analogy) to <i>wipe dry:</i> - wipe.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}